      <text>5</text>
    </field>
    <field name="Prerequisite"  table="yes"><text>No value</text></field>
    <field name="Location" table="yes">
      <text>Arm, Hand</text>
    </field>
    <field description="yes" name="Description">
      <text>One or more metal blades is inserted into the forearm. It can extend forward or swing out from the back of the arm. The blades are used with the small sword skill and can deal <roll><num>1</num><face>6</face><bOff>+</bOff><bns>2</bns><kind>S</kind></roll> </text>
    </field>
  </datum>
